snippet.title: Call of Juarez: The Cartel - Launch Trailer [US]
snippet.description: More videos on http://www.callofjuarez.com. Dismantle the gangs of the new wild west in single, co-op and multiplayer with the new shooter Call of Juarez: The Cartel. Playstation 3, Xbox 360 and PC.
